@c -*- texinfo -*-

@chapter Prompt Styles

Here you can find a preview of all included prompt styles.

@b{note:} in all screenshots the @code{Readline} option @code{show-editmode} was
active. The @@ at the start of the last prompt line indicates Emacs editmode, if
this option is disabled (default), the prompt lines start directly at the left.

